race.comment: RACCOON ROGER (1) profiles well and boxed nicely for his debut. Watch the betting closely for a strong push. FEDERAL HARRY (7) profiles nicely for his debut but has a wide box to overcome. Expected to feature on debut. PORT BEFORE BED (6) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (18.29) in a Maiden at this track. Can do much better this time. UNDER A SPELL (8) is a Michael Edwards-trained newcomer by Aston Rupee out of Witch Earner. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles well so watch market closely.
